= Story Guide =

'''Dragon Quest III''' (SNES) follows Ortega's child on a quest against Baramos.

__TOC__

== Premise ==

The legendary warrior Ortega died fighting the Archfiend Baramos. Now his child comes of age and must complete the quest to save the world.

